<verse sid="1KI 9:12"/>And Chiram departed from Tyre and went to Galilee, to see the cities that Salomon gave him, and they did not please him,<verse eid="1KI 9:12"/>

<verse sid="1KI 9:13"/>and he said, "What kind of cities are these that you gave me, brother?" And he called them Boundary to this day.<verse eid="1KI 9:13"/>

<verse sid="1KI 9:14"/>And Chiram brought Salomon one hundred twenty talents of gold,<verse eid="1KI 9:14"/>

