<verse sid="1KI 18:20"/>And Achaab sent to all Israel and gathered all the prophets at Mount Carmel.<verse eid="1KI 18:20"/>

<verse sid="1KI 18:21"/>And Eliou came near to all, and Eliou said to them, "How long will you go limping on both legs? If the Lord is God, go after him, but if Baal is he, go after him." And the people did not answer a word.<verse eid="1KI 18:21"/>

<verse sid="1KI 18:22"/>And Eliou said to the people, "I all alone am left over as prophet of the Lord, and Baal's prophets number four hundred fifty men, and the prophets of the grove, four hundred.<verse eid="1KI 18:22"/>

