<verse sid="1KI 20:7"/>And his wife Iezabel said to him, "Do you now thus act the king over Israel? Get up, eat bread, and be yourself, I will give you the vineyard of Nabouthai the Iezraelite."<verse eid="1KI 20:7"/>

