<verse sid="1KI 22:52"/>(51) And Ochozias son of Achaab reigned over Israel in Samaria in the seventeenth year of Iosaphat, king of Iouda, and he reigned in Israel two years.<verse eid="1KI 22:52"/>

<verse sid="1KI 22:53"/>(52) And he did what was evil in the sight of the Lord and walked in the way of Achaab his father and in the way of Iezabel his mother and in the sins of the house of Ieroboam son of Nabat, who made Israel sin.<verse eid="1KI 22:53"/>

